AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002162> "x is in taxon y if an only if y is an organism, and the relationship between x and y is one of: part of (reflexive), developmentally preceded by, derives from, secreted by, expressed.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002162> "in taxon")
SubObjectPropertyOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002162> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002320>)

