AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002215> "A relation between a material entity (such as a cell) and a process, in which the material entity has the ability to carry out the process. ")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002215> "capable of"@en)
